        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer71588476" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4935834747594846126">speculation is a grand endeavor - it both looses and gains meaning when it arises as satire. To do what Montesquieu has done before the arrival of modern media sources is amazing. While there are certain flaws and falsehoods throughout, this work looses no relevance in the modern world. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


